        "summary": "Creates a workspace creation job",
        "description": "Validates the request, checks permissions, auto-populates infrastructure fields, and creates a job for asynchronous workspace creation. Infrastructure fields (ResourcePool, SqlServer, etc.) are not accepted - they are always auto-populated with default values.",
